{"tid":2086264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣啟動「香港人道援助關懷行動專案」 總統蔡英文：不分政府民間 給港人最堅定支持","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T09:26:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eec7f4440afec0baf4079808f5d4fa813fc98cb5","tid":2086264,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/06/30/realtime/8113736.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F06%2F30%2Frealtime%2F8113736.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465&h=1c7e253c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖/翻攝自總統臉書<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文總統稍早在臉書發文表示，中國曾經承諾香港五十年不變，今天港版國安法的強行通過，不僅代表中國罔顧香港民意，背棄承諾，更證明了「一國兩制」不可行。因應變局，台灣將不分政府民間，共同協力，給予香港人民最堅定的支持。<br />\n<br />\n中國人大常委會今天通過港版的國安法，蔡總統上午出席公開活動後向媒體回應，下午更透過臉書發表看法。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統說，中國曾經承諾香港五十年不變，今天港版國安法的強行通過，不僅代表中國罔顧香港民意，背棄承諾，更證明了「一國兩制」不可行。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統表示，我們希望，香港人民可以持續堅持他們所珍惜的自由和人權。台灣也已經啟動「香港人道援助關懷行動專案」，對於需要協助的香港人民，將提供便捷的服務及基本照顧。<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統指出，政府援港專案的「台港服務交流辦公室」，將在明天正式營運。因應變局，台灣將不分政府民間，共同協力，給予香港人民最堅定的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4669016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F4669016&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2FwHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=3653be30\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4669016</a>"},{"pid":"9a836b9cb509dd65bbb92bf7d7867243f1cab016","tid":2086264,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d440518295cdc27a7f2363b6aca7e941d59aaf","tid":2086264,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"感謝台灣"},{"pid":"6f348f8232b9f28841f8b8eaacc2ad020c20a29b","tid":2086264,"uid":277934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}